score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T09:34:46.000Z","msg":"我仲記得小學果陣，我個friend(A)同另一個同學(B)打架。當時我係班長，咁我就從後捉住B嗌你地唔好打喇，而A係繼續打，B就比我捉住左。老師問起，我話我當時想分開佢地。"},{"pid":"a4347bc5aea224b63a656e17ed593b5a06124cbf","tid":1308521,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T09:36:28.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"2955a7f1f5aad92ee989c6181106ae0acb81bc3b","tid":1308521,"uid":269601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T10:37:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"46a707984a4858c54fe0f078e9360eb220b7fcd1","tid":1308521,"uid":62369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T11:29:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c78e9415183adc05aca0e3202d371d7c74acf41a","tid":1308521,"uid":80965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T13:55:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acedbdb28f574b1064e421943ce563d8f7ef9f8c","tid":1308521,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T13:55:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"86e2023d4dee874eca8e72b99aa997de1beba8e6","tid":1308521,"uid":162372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T14:01:06.000Z","msg":"pish 廢中廢老太衝動 優先考慮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c61afb752e58c9b35610885f00b518aafba024f","tid":1308521,"uid":215794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4fd4226984484b2001fcfe00d3bf85d811de1b8f","tid":1308521,"uid":39752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:13:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好捉住被打嘅人<br />\n特別係自己人俾人打嘅情況</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n勸交無錯係要分開雙方<br />\n但如果係自己人被打，你唔先從惡嗰邊去控制<br />\n你只係心理上慣性欺善怕惡，怕自己中埋招<br />\n而忘記咗另一邊被你控制嘅人先最需要安全<br />\n<br />\n睇過啲搭車啲廢老揮拳打學生哥追住嚟鬧嘅片<br />\n個學生哥一衝前就一定俾路人捉住撥開<br />\n相反啲廢老就鍾意行又得屌又得再揮空拳又得<br />\n我睇撚到黑人問號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可能有人驚個學生還拖就一齊中毆打罪<br />\n但你都唔撚係捉住個受害者俾人當沙包下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">出得嚟勸交你就唔好怯</span></strong><br />\n威脅太大拎晒老牛嘅你都唔敢出嚟啦<br />\n要勸交你控制住是但一方接觸唔到另一邊就得<br />\n不論你係用擋用推用捉甚至遮住佢視線<br />\n<br />\n咁如果尋晚南亞仔個情況又點呢<br />\n有人勸交只係撳住佢而無撳住個廢老<br />\n南亞仔想走又走唔到<br />\n個廢老起咗身又可以周圍走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n勸交你一個人只控制到其中一方係好合理<br />\n想控制邊個你可以小心選擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我就覺得俾人打嘅人需要靜靜休養係好合理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n舉遮個哥哥做咗個相對好嘅示範<br />\n遮住咗敵人視線同時無妨礙南亞仔行動<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">呢個原則並唔係鼓勵任何人打鬥<br />\n相反係保護緊自己人<br />\n即管放心去教你身邊嘅所有人</span></span></strong>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T14:20:55.000Z","msg":"真係專業推介啊"},{"pid":"42eb6f7e59962b8c2a4abc491cba7e0a0ad300f8","tid":1308521,"uid":213379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T14:21:30.000Z","msg":"七 月 十 三 ！光 復 上 水 ！踢 走 水 貨 客！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1310098\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1310098</a><br />\n<br />\n【推上熱門】713光復上水資料<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1309441\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1309441</a><br />\n<br />\n[714/721] 野餐及夢遊服飾<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1309156\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1309156</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中火力推Post</span></span>"},{"pid":"3e04ecb41b00b8fdc1588b392cf736d1a0266424","tid":1308521,"uid":39752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2506f9ae3601871abff97fa60cf1a131a42cde4e","tid":1308521,"uid":189799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T09:34:46.000Z","msg":"我仲記得小學果陣，我個friend(A)同另一個同學(B)打架。當時我係班長，咁我就從後捉住B嗌你地唔好打喇，而A係繼續打，B就比我捉住左。老師問起，我話我當時想分開佢地。"},"citedBy